Regions Names Protective Life CEO Johns to Board of Directors

-- B y   L a u r a   M a r c i n e k
-- 
2011-10-20T15:06:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-20/regions-names-protective-life-ceo-johns-to-board-of-directors.html
Regions Financial Corp. (RF) , the 10th
largest U.S. bank by deposits, named  Protective Life Corp. (PL)  Chief
Executive Officer John D. Johns to the lender’s board of
directors.  “His considerable experience in the insurance business
will bring a wealth of expertise and insight from the broader
financial services industry,” said Regions CEO Grayson Hall in
a statement today from the Birmingham, Alabama-based bank.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Laura Marcinek in New York at 
 Lmarcinek3@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  